If noone is seeding and you're a not too much of a newbie computer user, you can change this manually by opening "run" on the start menu, type "regedit", go to "[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\EA GAMES\Need for Speed Most Wanted]", double click "Language" and change it to whatever language you want. These languages are supported:
Danish
English
Finnish
French
German
Italian
Polish
Spanish
Swedish

if there is no string called "Language" in the folder, simply click edit > new > string and name it "Language"

if u cant download :
open the notepad 
type this 

Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\EA GAMES\Need for Speed Most Wanted]
"Language"="English"


and save as reg file . u can use ur desired language like Polish or any of the supported language simply by replcing it by english...

supportive language are Dannish,English,Finnish,Polish,French ,German,Italian,Spanish,Swedish.
